'''Charles Michael Detwiler''' (born March 6, 1947) is a former [[American football]] [[defensive back]] who played four seasons in the [[National Football League]] with the [[San Diego Chargers]] and [[Arizona Cardinals|St. Louis Cardinals]]. He played [[college football]] at [[Utah State University]] and attended [[Glendora High School]] in [[Glendora, California]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.profootballarchives.com/detw00200.html | title=CHUCK DETWILER | publisher=profootballarchives.com | accessdate=3 September 2014}}</ref> He was also a member of the [[The Hawaiians]] of the [[World Football League]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nasljerseys.com/WFL/Players/D/Detwiler.Chuck.htm | title=Chuck Detwiler | publisher=nasljerseys.com | accessdate=September 3, 2014}}</ref>

